    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce the maximum fine for non-payment of TV Licence",
        "additional_details": "People are being penalised for a service that they do not require. The Government has to abide by the BBC Charter until 2027 but the maximum fine should now be reduced to reflect current circumstances.",
        "background": "Amend the Communications Act 2003 to reduce the maximum fine payable on non-payment of the TV licence fee from \u00a31000 to \u00a310.",
